name: The Wolf king was released from prison and killed on the spot

metadata.name: Betrothal ceremony, unmarried pregnancy
metadata.description:
The king of the Wolf?



The young man frowned.



But the attitude of Nian general to Xiao Zhan, let his heart like death.



A major general, in the face of Xiao Zhan, incredibly humble, deferential, what does this mean? How is that possible? Could it be that this young general drove dozens of jeeps, with a team of 200 people, just to welcome Xiao Zhan out of prison?



Come 5 years, xiao zhan is not all the time be imprisoned in the spring city fourth prison?
